{"tid":2123155,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"遭冒名發電郵要求買儲值卡 徒孫極速識破騙局 資深大狀駱應淦：真係笨賊","createTime":"2020-07-24T12:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T12:50:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4d47b77fd9e8d6ceb6a32c8a45b0b05dd442c3","tid":2123155,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/VQNYEEZHPB3XMJCBXLTRIFZW7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FVQNYEEZHPB3XMJCBXLTRIFZW7Y%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZ0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=12acc774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FVQNYEEZHPB3XMJCBXLTRIFZW7Y%2F&h=3baebf98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/VQNYEEZHPB3XMJCBXLTRIFZW7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n打刑事案逾40年的資深大律師駱應淦，最近遭電郵騙徒冒認，向在同一辦事處上班的「徒孫」發訊息，要求徒孫購買面值共5,000元的儲值禮物卡，並將卡上兌換密碼拍照傳送。徒孫與同門大狀同事討論後，極速識破騙局，並向駱應淦匯報事件，駱隨即知會大律師公會，並且報警處理。駱應淦今接受《蘋果》查詢時笑稱騙徒是「笨賊」，謂「個個都知我係『高科技』人士」。駱的徒弟亦風趣表示，若騙徒以代買香煙作幌子冒認師公師父，可信度會更高。"},{"pid":"6d3fd61ca46af4d3b2c90e0c9b24b7b744eef7b2","tid":2123155,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d67a6213cbfa08e767700d516fcfc552979922","tid":2123155,"uid":34869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:25:22.000Z","msg":"徒孫與同門閂埋房門可能有傾過驚係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18004fcc04cf1d61a17bd79e01b7e9907c2fda54","tid":2123155,"uid":49044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c3d67a6213cbfa08e767700d516fcfc552979922"